snippet.textDisplay:
coke studio has done more than composing a song today. I am a kathiyawadi(from the province where kirtidan belongs) since my early childhood i was always attracted to my folk music. even after growing up, my choice never met with any of my friend or collegue when it comes to music.

for them it was "bhajan". they all were completly into heavy metal, english country, hip hop n stuff. i dont disrespect their choice, but then now i can seriously make them feel "THE POWER OF FOLK MUSIC, RAW MUSIC"! 

LONG LIVE SACHIN AND TEAM!
snippet.textOriginal:
coke studio has done more than composing a song today. I am a kathiyawadi(from the province where kirtidan belongs) since my early childhood i was always attracted to my folk music. even after growing up, my choice never met with any of my friend or collegue when it comes to music.

for them it was "bhajan". they all were completly into heavy metal, english country, hip hop n stuff. i dont disrespect their choice, but then now i can seriously make them feel "THE POWER OF FOLK MUSIC, RAW MUSIC"!
